sentences: Hanna Lindblad (born 13 October 1980 in Motala) is a Swedish singer.
After studying music at Hammar High School in Sandviken, Lindblad went to Balettakademien in Gothenburg, from which she graduated in 2000.
She was nominated for a Guldmasken for her role in "Saturday Night Fever".
She participated in the second Semi-Final of Melodifestivalen 2010 in Sandviken where she achieved fifth place with her song Manipulated.
She participated in the fourth Semi-Final of Melodifestivalen 2012 with the song "Goosebumps".
